        <!-- About Content Section -->
        <section class="about-content-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <h2>Our Story</h2>
                        <p>चित्रम् (Chitram) was born from a simple yet powerful vision: to create a bridge between digital artists and art enthusiasts in Nepal and beyond. Our platform celebrates the rich tradition of Nepalese art while embracing the limitless possibilities of digital creativity.</p>
                        
                        <p>In Sanskrit, "चित्रम्" means "wonderful" or "picture" - and that's exactly what we aim to showcase. Every artwork on our platform tells a story, captures an emotion, or sparks imagination.</p>
                        
                        <blockquote class="motivation-quote">
                            <p>"Art is not what you see, but what you make others see."</p>
                            <cite>- Edgar Degas</cite>
                        </blockquote>
                        
                        <div class="features-list">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                <span>Curated collection of high-quality digital artworks</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                <span>Direct support for emerging and established artists</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                <span>Secure platform for art transactions</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                                <span>Community-driven art discovery</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541961017774-22349e4a1262?w=500&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" alt="Artist at work" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
